METAL PACKAGES INDUSTRIES
TECHNICAL DATA SHEET: COSMETIC & BEAUTY ALUMINIUM COLLAPSIBLE TUBES

1. PRODUCT DESCRIPTION
Aesthetic, eco-friendly, and premium-feeling aluminium collapsible tubes designed for cosmetic products, hair color creams, skin lotions, and high-end beauty formulations.

2. SPECIFICATIONS & DIMENSIONS
- Diameter Range: 16.0 mm to 40.0 mm
- Wall Thickness: 0.12 mm - 0.18 mm
- Capacity: 10 ml to 100 ml
- Purity: 99.7% pure refined aluminium slugs
- Shoulder Type: Smooth shoulder / Coated shoulder options

3. DECORATION & PRINTING
- Printing Process: 6-color offset printing with high resolution brand reproduction
- Top Varnish: Glossy, Semi-Matte, or Full Matte luxury finish
- Base Coat: Premium base coating for smooth exterior texture

4. ACCESSORIES & CAPPING
- Caps: Conical caps, Octagonal caps, stand-up wide caps, ribbed caps
- Material: High-density Polypropylene (PP) / Polyethylene (PE)
- Nozzle options: Open nozzle / Sealed membrane (piercing cap required)

5. SUSTAINABILITY
- 100% Recyclable and eco-friendly packaging
- Infinite recyclability without degradation of material properties

